RT-Extension-MandatorySubject - Enforce users to fill the subject when creating a ticket

This RT Extension enforces users to fill the subject when creating a ticket via
the web interface.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Then, to make it active, add it to @Plugins in RT site configuration file
(RT_SiteConfig.pm), example:

    Set(@Plugins,(qw(RT::Extension::MandatorySubject)));

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

You can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc RT::Extension::MandatorySubject


You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
