    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/RT-Extension-MandatorySubject

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/RT-Extension-MandatorySubject

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/RT-Extension-MandatorySubject


